This model sits upright, like the [[ZyXEL NBG5715]]. All antennas in the device are internal.
"WRTB-283N_V03" and "ESK-A03-9703R" is silkscreened on the board in the FCC photos.
Part numbers, per the FCC internal photos, follow... *SoC: BCM4718A1KFBG *RAM: H5PS5162GFR-S6C *5GHz radio: BCM4331KMLG **The 5GHz radio is using 3x [http://www.skyworksinc.com/Product.aspx?ProductID=955 '''Skyworks''' ('''SiGe''') SE2594L Dual Band FEM]s. *GbE Switch: BCM53115MKFBG
Possible 20:10:7A OUI (it's on a MAC label affixed to the device in the FCC ''manual'')..
